{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775875211590,"sessionID":"ses_285995f58ffe7A06Rb3mqAo6n0","part":{"id":"prt_d7a693d780014WVZEwpY5Ej8OD","messageID":"msg_d7a6934b7001CcJEYAz2PJubTo","sessionID":"ses_285995f58ffe7A06Rb3mqAo6n0","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_5ba0d3df4ff84b3086a0c568","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/project.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/project.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AgentCube — OpenSpec Project Context\n2: \n3: > Source: [github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube](https://github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube)\n4: > Generated: 2026-03-21 (from source tree reverse-engineering)\n5: \n6: ## Purpose\n7: \n8: AgentCube is a Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents.\n9: It provisions isolated sandbox pods on demand, routes HTTP traffic to them through\n10: session-aware proxies, and manages their lifecycle (creation, expiry, idle cleanup).\n11: \n12: ## Tech Stack\n13: \n14: | Layer | Technology |\n15: |-------|-----------|\n16: | Language (server) | Go 1.24, module `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` |\n17: | Language (CLI/SDK) | Python ≥3.10 |\n18: | HTTP framework | Gin (Go), Typer (Python CLI), FastAPI (example) |\n19: | Kubernetes | CRDs (`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`), controller-runtime, `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox` |\n20: | Storage | Redis (go-redis/v9), Valkey (valkey-go) |\n21: | Auth | JWT RS256 (golang-jwt/v5), K8s TokenReview |\n22: | Packaging | Helm 3, multi-stage Docker, GitHub Actions CI/CD |\n23: | Docs | Docusaurus 3.x |\n24: \n25: ## Architecture\n26: \n27: ```\n28: Client / SDK / CLI\n29:   → Router (Deployment :8080)\n30:      ↔ Redis/Valkey (session store)\n31:      → WorkloadManager (Service :8080)\n32:         ↔ Redis/Valkey\n33:         → K8s API: CRDs, Sandbox, Pod, Secret, TokenReview\n34:   Sandbox Pods (with optional PicoD daemon)\n35:   Agentd (idle cleanup controller)\n36:   Optional: Volcano vc-agent-scheduler\n37: ```\n38: \n39: ## Conventions\n40: \n41: - Go packages under `pkg/`, binaries under `cmd/`\n42: - Python CLI at `cmd/cli/`, SDK at `sdk-python/`\n43: - JSON tags use camelCase; Go structs use PascalCase\n44: - K8s resources use `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` API group\n45: - Normative language: SHALL = mandatory, SHOULD = recommended, MAY = optional\n\n(End of file - total 45 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AgentCube — OpenSpec Project Context\n\n> Source: [github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube](https://github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube)\n> Generated: 2026-03-21 (from source tree reverse-engineering)\n\n## Purpose\n\nAgentCube is a Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents.\nIt provisions isolated sandbox pods on demand, routes HTTP traffic to them through\nsession-aware proxies, and manages their lifecycle (creation, expiry, idle cleanup).\n\n## Tech Stack\n\n| Layer | Technology |\n|-------|-----------|\n| Language (server) | Go 1.24, module `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` |\n| Language (CLI/SDK) | Python ≥3.10 |\n| HTTP framework | Gin (Go), Typer (Python CLI), FastAPI (example) |\n| Kubernetes | CRDs (`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`), controller-runtime, `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox` |\n| Storage | Redis (go-redis/v9), Valkey (valkey-go) |","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/project.md","time":{"start":1775875211584,"end":1775875211589}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775875212925,"sessionID":"ses_285995f58ffe7A06Rb3mqAo6n0","part":{"id":"prt_d7a6941cd001Bk7iiDjeqGJb1l","messageID":"msg_d7a6934b7001CcJEYAz2PJubTo","sessionID":"ses_285995f58ffe7A06Rb3mqAo6n0","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_55456c64130e40cbbed3b797","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-032/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-032/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-032 — Dockerfile 多阶段构建 (3 images) — Tasks\n2: \n3: > **Module:** docker\n4: > **Language:** Dockerfile\n5: > **Size:** S\n6: > **Precondition:** <!-- TODO: e.g. Stage ST-3 (Design) completed -->\n7: > **Reference:** `changes/AR-032/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-032/design.md`, `changes/AR-032/delta-spec.md`\n8: > **Dependency:** <!-- TODO: list dependencies -->\n9: \n10: ---\n11: \n12: ## T-001: <!-- TODO: Task title -->\n13: \n14: <!-- TODO: Task checklist items -->\n15: \n16: **验收**: <!-- TODO: Acceptance verification command -->\n17: \n18: ---\n19: \n20: ## Dependency Graph\n21: \n22: <!-- TODO: Add dependency graph -->\n23: \n24: ## Parallelizable Groups\n25: \n26: <!-- TODO: List parallelizable task groups -->\n27: \n28: | Group | Tasks | Prerequisites |\n29: |-------|-------|---------------|\n30: | <!-- TODO --> | <!-- TODO --> | <!-- TODO --> |\n31: \n32: ---\n33: \n34: ## Acceptance Criteria\n35: \n36: <!-- TODO: List acceptance criteria with verification commands -->\n37: \n38: | # | Criterion | Command |\n39: |---|-----------|---------|\n40: | <!-- TODO --> | <!-- TODO --> | <!-- TODO --> |\n\n(End of file - total 40 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-032 — Dockerfile 多阶段构建 (3 images) — Tasks\n\n> **Module:** docker\n> **Language:** Dockerfile\n> **Size:** S\n> **Precondition:** <!-- TODO: e.g. Stage ST-3 (Design) completed -->\n> **Reference:** `changes/AR-032/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-032/design.md`, `changes/AR-032/delta-spec.md`\n> **Dependency:** <!-- TODO: list dependencies -->\n\n---\n\n## T-001: <!-- TODO: Task title -->\n\n<!-- TODO: Task checklist items -->\n\n**验收**: <!-- TODO: Acceptance verification command -->\n\n---\n\n## Dependency Graph","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-032/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775875212917,"end":1775875212923}}}}
